{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/paintWorklet\"><code>paintWorklet (Static property)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape\"><code>escape()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/supports\"><code>supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>The <code><strong>CSS</strong></code> interface holds useful CSS-related methods. No objects with this interface are implemented: it contains only static methods and is&nbsp;therefore a utilitarian interface.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The CSS interface is a utility interface and no object of this type can be created: only static properties are defined on it.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"static_properties","title":"Static properties","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"css.paintworklet_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/paintWorklet\"><code>CSS.paintWorklet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;<svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>Provides access to the Worklet responsible for all the classes&nbsp;related to painting.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The CSS interface is a utility interface and no object of this type can be created: only static methods are defined on it.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"static_methods","title":"Static methods","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>No inherited static methods</em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"css.registerproperty_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/RegisterProperty\"><code>CSS.registerProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Registers <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/--*\"><code>custom properties</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, allowing for property type checking, default values, and properties that do or do not&nbsp;inherit their value.</dd>\n <dt id=\"css.supports_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/supports\"><code>CSS.supports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> indicating if the pair <em>property-value</em>, or the condition, given in parameter is supported.</dd>\n <dt id=\"css.escape\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/escape\"><code>CSS.escape()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Can be used to escape a string mostly&nbsp;for use as part of a CSS selector.</dd>\n <dt id=\"css_factory_functions_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions\"><code>CSS factory functions</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Can be used to return a new <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\">CSSUnitValue</a></code> with a value of the parameter number of the units of the name of the factory function method used.</dd>\n <dd>\n <pre class=\"notranslate\">CSS.em(3) // CSSUnitValue {value: 3, unit: \"em\"}</pre>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.css-houdini.org/css-paint-api-1/#dom-css-paintworklet\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Painting API Level 1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'paintWorklet' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Adds the <code>paintWorklet</code> static property.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-css.escape()-method\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSS' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Adds the <code>escape()</code> static method.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/#the-css-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSS' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Anwärter Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSS","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See Also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See Also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The CSS interface holds useful CSS-related methods. No objects with this interface are implemented: it contains only static methods and is therefore a utilitarian interface.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/css","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/css/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS","title":"CSS"}],"pageTitle":"CSS - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}